OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FShowery rain
OL,6,Farriving this evening, clearing
OL,7,Fsouthwards by the early hours with
OL,8,Fskies clearing overnight. Turning
OL,9,Fchilly with a touch of frost in the
OL,10,Fcountryside. Winds falling light.
OL,11,
OL,12,CThursday:FA much brighter day with a
OL,13,Fmixture of sunny periods and
OL,14,Foccasional cloudier spells. Staying
OL,15,Fgenerally dry until after dark. Cooler
OL,16,Fthan on Wednesday but pleasantly warm
OL,17,Fin the sunshine.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
