OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:
OL,6,FChangeable with showers possible at
OL,7,Ftimes, these most likely on Good
OL,8,FFriday. Often windy with the strongest
OL,9,Fwinds on Saturday. Plenty of dry
OL,10,Fweather too with warm sunny spells.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
